Package: iNEXT.4steps
Type: Package
Title: four steps of INterpolation and EXTrapolation analysis
Version: 1.1.0
Author: Anne Chao and Kai-Hsiang Hu
Maintainer: Kai-Hsiang Hu <river19951224@gmail.com>
Description: Provides simple functions to compute and plot a complete analysis process
             with following four steps:
             <Step1>Sample completeness profiles.
             <Step2>Asymptotic analysis.
             <Step3>Non-asymptotic coverage-based rarefaction and extrapolation analysis.
             <Step4>Evenness among species abundances.
             (You can find the paper(No.135) from Chao.website:
             http://chao.stat.nthu.edu.tw/wordpress/publication-list/)
License: GPL (>= 3)
Imports:
        devtools,
        iNEXT,
        gridExtra,
        ggplot2,
        reshape2,
        dplyr,
        stats
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
